{"tid":1755350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子青龍頭高處墮下","createTime":"2019-11-25T14:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T14:35:14.000Z","uid":211578,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd909447915ca0701de9e4f7920390000b2f10ee","tid":1755350,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:11:18.000Z","msg":"青龍頭有人從高處墮下，今日(25日)早上10時55分，青山公路100號豪景花園，突然傳出巨響，途人聞聲上前查看，發現一名男子倒臥屋苑對開空地，奄奄一息，於是報警求助。救護員趕至，經檢查後證實男子當場死亡。<br />\n警員在場未有檢獲遺書，其後聯絡死者家屬調查，證實事主姓盧(34歲)，初步相信他由上址一單位墮下，事件沒有可疑，惟事主死因有待驗屍確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191125/mobile/bkn-20191125125134928-1125_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191125%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191125125134928-1125_00822_001.html&d=yZvzIFdj7oCTZXRWgogUmVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=ca2c2a84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191125/mobile/bkn-20191125125134928-1125_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n點解淨係得東網報新聞？"},{"pid":"d190f9a60c941d05bebb8c9d5ee2c44c3ee2bdc5","tid":1755350,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:11:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2c02eb5d8b0217020324e548ea89489f7869991","tid":1755350,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:34:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Mon post狗你地做過咩你地自己知</span></span>"},{"pid":"f2d9a7044dc6e15702d2a435e57d3cbdfdb4a370","tid":1755350,"uid":303677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}